Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.44,0:29:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.54,0:29:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抽的什麼簽
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.78,0:29:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}某種意義上也是很厲害呢…
